12:25.282 --> 12:25.503
Yeah.

12:26.083 --> 12:27.706
Her book must still be in print, right?

12:29.309 --> 12:32.134
I'm sure it must be.

12:32.154 --> 12:33.616
I'm sure I can get one at Waterstones.

12:33.896 --> 12:37.022
Yeah.

12:37.563 --> 12:38.144
Anyway.

12:38.164 --> 12:38.464
Yeah.

